name: TellMeanAlternativeFact

des:
The world is tired of facts, of mundane truth. This skill, created in response to this trend, gives Alexa the ability to tell you an interesting, "unique" alternative fact! 

Features:
Tells you a 100% valid, simple "alternative" fact
Over 448 "alternative" facts
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
